From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Mon, 16 Feb 2026 17:34:32 +1100
Subject: [PATCH] firmware: arm_scmi: Add ACPI boot support for CIX Sky1

Add ACPI shared memory discovery, mailbox channel validation,
and ACPI boot support for the SCMI firmware transport on Sky1.
---
 drivers/firmware/Kconfig                      |  1 +
 drivers/firmware/Makefile                     |  1 +
 drivers/firmware/arm_scmi/bus.c               |  3 +
